d, will be unobtainable after the end of event)","When the tide goes out, it always leaves special gifts for the beach. (Event limited, will be unobtainable after the end of event)","Looking to end things? Come on... Encore! Encore! (Event limited, will be unobtainable after the end of event)","\"Winning this hand can keep you lucky for a whole year. I\'m not lying nyaa.\" (Event limited, will be unobtainable after the end of event)","Another storm has come. (Event limited, will be unobtainable after the end of event)","Again and again, fate will play out in the same way. (Event limited, will be unobtainable after the end of event)","The killer move of Cat Warrior Ichihime, aimed to interrupt ultimate skills like Thirteen Orphans or Nine Gates. (Event limited, will be unobtainable after the end of event)","A swordsman who once fought with Kazuha Saionji left the following remark on her sword: \"Like a tiger storming down the mountain, fierce, swift and difficult to guard.\"","Evergreen mistletoe brings love and hope to its holder, not just this Ron~ (Event limited, will be unobtainable after the end of event)","A gentle breeze blow past the trees in February, the plum blossoms in the garden enrich the scenery. (Event limited, will be unobtainable after the end of event)","Via electromagnetic induction, Mahjong tiles are shot at 3 times the speed of sound, striking all opponents like heaven\'s wrath, as well as taking all their points. (Event limited, will be unobtainable after the end of event)","When you realize something isn\'t right, you are already deep in this icy trap.","A duck just descended from heaven, squeak! (Event limited, will be unobtainable after the end of event)","Accurate movements in parts will lead to victory in whole, this is the winning philosophy of the mechanic world. (Event limited, will be unobtainable after the end of event)","Ninpo, the throat-sealing technique! (Event limited, will be unobtainable after the end of event)","Even blessed by three thousand rays, flowers will fade in autumn.","Prophecied to take place within reality, an absolute realm from which no matter can escape.","It\'s not just cool special effects, as it can also cut the celebratory cake into six perfectly equal slices.","The winning falls from the heavenly waterfall, accept this victory and enjoy the moment.","The bats are here to claim your soul, or... to peek at your hand...","\"Beep—beep— The system has detected a Riichi crisis! Players, please take immediate actions! This is an emergency!\" (Event limited, will be unobtainable after the end of event)","Now that you have signed a magical pact with me, the stars will guide you to the right path. (Event limited, will be unobtainable after the end of event)","\"If I can spin fast enough, no one can be as cool as me!\" (Event limited, will be unobtainable after the end of event)","Look, what\'s that twinkling in the sky... (Event limited, will be unobtainable after the end of event)","Once picked up, the bloody silhouette of the Lance of Longinus can never be put down. (Event limited, will be unobtainable after the end of event)","Justice may be late, but it will always come in the end. (Event limited, will be unobtainable after the end of event)","The witch\'s charming words linger in your mind like butterflies. She said... (Event limited, will be unobtainable after the end of event)","Listen! That\'s the sound of waves \"Riichi\"ing on the rocks! (Event limited, will be unobtainable after the end of event)","DJ, drop the beat! (Event limited, will be unobtainable after the end of event)","\"Riichi, 1 Han.\" Don\'t let go a single chance of gaining Han. (Event limited, will be unobtainable after the end of event)","\"You have reached your destination, Riichi Twister Bubble Tea Shop. Thank you for using Mahjong Soul Virtual Navigation.\" (Event limited, will be unobtainable after the end of event)","Summons a Riichi Demon once and grants the probability to obtain Ippatsu. (Event limited, will be unobtainable after the end of event)","\"7 scra...slashes per second is Ichihime\'s unique skill, nyaa!\" (Event limited, will be unobtainable after the end of event)","The tiger\'s howl is both a declaration and a warning. From now on, you need to pay attention to every move.","The gift from Santa will never miss out and often appears when you least expect it. It may be a pastry, a chance meeting, or even a Ron after Riichi~ (Event limited, will be unobtainable after the end of event)","In the darkness, the fragrance of the plum blossoms encircles you just as the wind of the new year rises. (Event limited, will be unobtainable after the end of event)","Legends say a yellow creature lives in the witch\'s forest. They can create a special electric effect together. The Red Panda Squad has replicated this effect with an offensive magic spell. (Event limited, will be unobtainable after the end of event)","If you keep accepting her aid, you will be left with no recourse in the end.","A flock of ducks is swimming across the Mahjong table. (Event limited, will be unobtainable after the end of event)","A super intelligent quantum computer has entered the battlefield, Riichi confirmed, Ippatsu ready to go!(Event limited, will be unobtainable after the end of event)","Ninpo, the war-declaring technique!(Event limited, will be unobtainable after the end of event)","I dare wager with the gods, for a chance to claim your heart.","How Ichihime shows she\'s been to somewhere is unique.","One should ask themselves three questions each day: Do you call Chii? Do you call Pon? Do you declare Riichi?","People hit by snowballs get double the luck, and the points.","A sprout to become something unknown.","Default portrait frame.","A reward for Mahjong Soul official tournament winner. (Expires in 1 year)","A certificate of excellent performer on Path of Trial.","A certificate of outstanding performer on Path of Trial.","A certificate of unparalleled grandmaster on Path o