 Wait, did I just find out some secret that I shouldn\'t know? (Event limited, will be unobtainable after the end of event)","Let’s make a snowman on this snowy night! (Event limited, will be unobtainable after the end of event)","Fireworks crackles as loud as mahjong tiles. Chii brings victory as well as Pon. (Event limited, will be unobtainable after the end of event)","\"One, two, three... nine carps in total! If Chiori wants them, then I, Riu, will catch them all you!\" (Event limited, will be unobtainable after the end of event)","The Brave Cat is fearless. Whether faced with enemies hidden in the palace or rivals sitting in front of the Mahjong table, Cat Warrior Ichihime will always forge ahead without a care. (Event limited, will be unobtainable after the end of event)","Flames in the fireplace make a cracking sound from time to time, as if cheering for this intense match. Nothing can beat playing Mahjong in a cozy room on Christmas Eve~ (Event limited, will be unobtainable after the end of event)","As bunny, kitty, lamb and riichi bets jump out of the limitless pouch, it\'s almost like a Blessing of Heaven could jump out soon too. (Event limited, will be unobtainable after the end of event)","The most wondrous scenery appears during the short moment when day meets night.","\"Now I\'m mad, nyaa!\" Bonus content exclusive to Mahjong Soul Pon☆ Blu-ray Disc.","One of the famed \"Thirty-six Views of One Han City\" paintings. (Event limited, will be unobtainable after the end of event)","\"Why is a raven like a writing desk?\" (Event limited, will be unobtainable after the end of event)","桌布-RML联赛（有效期至2023年6月1日0:00）","After hearing that there are fish so big that one won\'t fit into the pan in the sea, Ichihime overcame her inherent dislike for water and dived into the ocean.","The path to Celestrial starts here.","Invite the Moon to be your opponent, tour Mahjong dojos in spirit, the tiles you discard become flowers, then return home after winning.","Leave your house at midnight, and you might encounter a special mahjong partner.","The hanging wisteria is blooming in a delightful purple.","A table style.","A table style.","To call or not to call? There is never enough time to think.","It\'s only natural wanting to extend your hand into the water when you sense something happening under the surface.","...They say the speed of a falling sakura petal is about five centimeters per second.","Watermelon and ice cream are the fundamental respect for summer!","The sky is clear, and red leaves flutter.","As the snow covers everywhere, here comes a new year.","An arrangement of \"Early Spring Cherry Blossoms\". Bonus content exclusive to Mahjong Soul Pon☆ Blu-ray Disc.","2023 Mystery Gacha Commemoration","Mahjong fun is the real fun!","At the Orchid Pavilion, the literati are having a winding stream party to relaxing music and rustling flowers. (Event limited, will be unobtainable after the end of event)","The killing intent disguises itself in the tranquility.(Event limited, will be unobtainable after the end of event)","A silent encirclement, destroying everything hindering the Jyanshi\'s advance.","Indulge in the delight of this moment.","The harmonious melody can ease up the tension on the mahjong table, which is helpful for maintaining physical and mental health.","What kind of future will this game lead to?","Riichi music \"Splendid Dreams\". Changes the background music when you declare Riichi.","Every year when sakura blossoms, people will visit the shrine to offer Ichihime their delicious foods. What’s all that about? Nyaa~","Summer Theme Background","Christmas Carnival Exclusive\nWinter is the quietest season in Mahjong Soul Temple.","Mahjong Festival - Beach Party Event Exclusive\n\"Wow... The sea is here-nya!\" Enjoying Mahjong in the sea breeze is the best way to spend a hot summer day.","Autumn Theme Background","At the beginning of the new year, the immaculately cleaned Mahjong Soul Shrine awaits the arrival of Jyanshi Sama in the first rays of dawn.","You can almost hear the sound of flowing water just by looking at this scene. Hm? Is there something moving in the stream?","Even though the noise of fireworks is deafening, Ichihime is still sleeping soundly. Aren\'t you envious of her sleep quality?","These light spots floating at nighttime are tirelessly helping people find the dreams they lost during daytime.","Maybe Santa doesn\'t exist, but there are always people who love you.","In the golden dance hall illuminated by the gentle morning light, a beautiful melody is playing, waiting for someone to dance in it.","A sunny day and a rainbow... All things bright and beautiful are here.","At the end of the road lives a fairy, who is waiting for you to cross the flower fields to welcome the summer day.","The finest Christmas, the coolest present, for the champion that\'s you! And don\'t forget, try for the biggest winning hand in tonight\'s match!","With the beginning of the new year, everything is starting anew, and the well wishes have arrived in droves. Please accept these heartfelt blessings!","Chinese knots representing Four Big Winds, spring couplets with the characters of Thirteen Orphans, paper window flowers with the pattern of Nine Gates... Yep, this year will definitely be an auspicious one as well!","Spring couplets, all set! Dinner material, ready! New year\'s speech, finished! Lion dance performance, good to... Oh no! Today is another day of Ichihime trying to do the lion dance and ending up setting off the firecrackers. Looks like you have to be the one to finish the new year preparation this time!","Instead of raising cups amid a ruckus, having some snacks in a quiet corner is much more comfortable.","The result of a scuffle between high heels and the sole is that Master gets a one-day trip to the infirmary.","CODE GEASS Lelouch of the Rebellion X Mahjong Soul Collab Commemoration","Warm sunlight, milk tea with the right temperature and sweetness, delicious desserts, and you. Everything is just perfect.","Traditional ninjutsu vs modern technology, what an unusual battle to see in real life. Let\'s predict who will win this time!","The adventurers are very interested in the words you muttered in your sleep: Thirteen Orphans, Single-wait Four Concealed Triplets, and True Nine Gates. They wonder, are these magic spells from another world?","According to the \"Personal Meaningless Rankings\", the title of the fasted sleeper has been won by Yuzu. Now, who will get second place?","Ninjas should avoid the camera, but celebratory commemoration photos are the exception.","Under the calm surface, the world below is surprisingly colorful.","The gentle sea breeze enhances the summer vibe. Let\'s have fun together at the beach.","The moonlight sets off the charm of the beauties even when the flowers are no more.","It\'s said, \"The most dangerous place is the safest.\" But people tend to forget that the most dangerous place is literally the most dangerous... Gotcha!","Fate/kaleid liner Prisma Illya X Mahjong Soul Collab Commemoration","The right atmosphere! Optimal lighting! Perfect pose! Now, click the shutter, or the sincere smiles of the girls might turn sour if they need to stay still for too long...","Authentication Test: Please identify and tap all the \"cats\" in the picture. Congratulations, your hand speed surpassed 99% of the citizens! Please accept this Certificate for Excellent Citizens of One Han City!","It\'s great to be a gourmet in One Han City as huge feasts are held for every festival. The girls are on their way to achieving a grand slam in food, so as their \"owner,\" you are sure to get \"grand slams\" in your life as well!","Companionship may not be the most exciting gesture of love, but it is the most sincere and long-lasting one. May you always be happy and healthy, with love in your life in the years to come.","The girls are the most brilliant with your attention on them.","Reminder from the gal: Don\'t forget to keep hydrated in the hot spring!","Moonlight, like water, reflects all the beautiful things in the world.","Blue Archive X Mahjong Soul Collab Commemoration","Are you ready? Next up is the unmissable divine stage!","Amidst the sound of roaring engines, the victor is greeted with cheers.","Physical Ron attack and Magical Tsumo attack, which would work better on the mahjong table?","Seize the day, and enjoy your passion.","Gentle waves brush the beach, and seabirds sing, composing an anthem unique to the holiday paradise.","Fireworks bloom across the sky, and the party roars before your eyes.","Even if you lose the invitation, it\'s no big deal; after all, you are the main star of the party.","Don\'t be nervous, just report the results truthfully. She has always been fair with rewards and punishments.","Moonlight like water, pure as a dream; laughter fills the room, fragrance in the gleam.","Sanrio characters X Mahjong Soul Collab Commemoration","Two girls, ensnared in blooming blue roses, are waiting for their destined savior.","THE IDOLM@STER SHINY COLORS × Mahjong Soul Collab Commemoration Illustration","Sweat, blushes, and heartbeats! The girls\' game is on fire!","Spring\'s rosy glow begins the year anew, as garments\' fragrance charms the moments too.","Three people might feel a bit awkward, but with you, we\'ve got a full mahjong table!","May beauty endure, and fortune remain true.","Till we meet again, may your nights be sweet.","They say when the midnight bell tolls, a fairy\'s magic wanes... But a witch\'s power is unlimited. So, this Jyanshi, it seems it\'s time to change your dancing partner.","Given the situation we\'re in, it\'s totally understandable to put mahjong on the back burner for a bit.","Fireworks mark her pages, and you see sparks fly in her quiet eyes.","Mahjong Soul X THE MOVIE Fate/stay night [Heaven\'s Feel] Collab Commemoration Illustration","The dancers seem more nervous backstage than the audience out front for this long-awaited show. As the stand-in manager, it\'s up to you to lift their spirits!","Her eyes hold the dusk, awaiting a reunion that transcends time and space.","The gentle laughter of the girls and the sweet scent of cake fill the sun-soaked afternoon.","Fireworks, an evening breeze, a single heartbeat. This moment, forever ours.","Beneath the scorching summer sun, nothing is more precious than the cool kiss of a sea breeze.","As the seasons turn from green to gold, the silent sword\'s long tale is retold.","Mahjong Soul × Gintama Collab Commemoration Illustration","There is still so much of the world to see... Take my hand, and let our next journey begin.","As the mist leaves the crystal ball, a dragon\'s dream from a faraway world of snow appears.","Lucky treats for a fresh chapter. Wishing you a year that\'s tasty, fun, and full of good fortune!","\"Hehe. Yubai\'s sleeping face is cute, right?\nShh... don\'t wake her. Let\'s share some secrets, just you and me.\"","Red paper cut into festive shapes, soft brushstrokes tracing the first blooms of spring. May the years ahead be filled with joy, and bring you all the best this world has to offer.","Running through the streets or soaking up the festival vibes? Whatever you choose, it\'s the right call. This is your year to dream big and aim high – fortune will follow wherever you go.","Nyaa... I wonder what kinds of wishes everyone made for the new year...?","The whole street is blurred in lantern light, have you found the one you are searching for?","As today is Christmas Eve, running wild once in a while is not a bad thing.","On this pleasant summer afternoon, come with us to search for the Treasure of Anca Ranch!","The winner of this mahjong match will get the privilege to use the air conditioner and eat ice cream freely! Showdown!","From the tarot reading, the next few days won\'t be boring, let\'s look forward to the destined future","\"Don\'t just sit there, come feel the breath of the ocean with me, junior!\"","With the popping of the confetti, the celebration party has started!","Though the fireworks flash and disappear, the wonderful memories stay with us.","Asaha High School\'s costume party is in full swing, let the witch and wizard be your guide!","When the world is covered in white, the one you loved sure is waiting for you.","If you ask where the best spot is for watching the fireworks, the answer is of course the Mahjong Soul Shrine!","A plate of snacks, a pot of tea, a table for mahjong, and the night is on!","A bird is singing on the willow\'s frostless branch, but the leaves hide half of its figure. The precious spring will make your misfortune go away and replace it with good luck.","\"Shhh— Just enjoy a night like this.\"","You\'re worried about sweating? Just go into the hot spring again after the ping pong match!","It\'s 3 PM! You know the drill, coffee first!","\"Today\'s patrol starts with protecting the butterflies. Follow Yuzu and don\'t get lost, OK?\"","Before a pajama party, a gal needs a makeover with friends.","\"We are on our way to the beach, meeting you here must be fate. How about joining us?\"","\"Hehe, don\'t forget what you are about to do because of my dazzling figure~\"","\"The summer festival\'s celebration cake of course needs an abundance of dried fish in it, like, at least four more, nyaa!\"","It\'s said that sky lanterns can bring people\'s wishes to heaven where they will be heard and fulfilled by the gods.","\"O Great Lord of the Night, may I... enjoy your company by myself?\"","Share the beauty of the moment with the floating glow and enshrouding haze.","Don\'t look so sad. Think of this as a short breather in a long journey. I\'ll see you again soon.","Look! Tiles are dancing with the lightning and thunder!","With the glow of the moon, the flower blooms magnificently.","I was born for Taco. I cannot live without it!","Indulge yourself in the peacefulness and relaxation at this moment.","It is said that anyone with this miraculous penguin can become stronger!","The gears\' rattling sounds are proof that the Wheel of Fortune is spinning.","Embrace the glory of victory or face the shame of defeat—it\'s all up to such a fragile card.","Does the journey between life or death ends in heaven or hell?","The unparalleled flower blooms on the table of calculation.","The highborn with both brains and brawn rule the realm of red and black.","Whispers of today\'s victory.","The strike of good fortune descends amid hellfire.","The key to victory is the willingness to risk everything to fight for a chance to win.","The legends of that one night continue to be told to this day.","The strong ones have no need to hide the sharpness of their claws.","A sudden confession.","A clear shot with great precision.","Keep a cool head even in love.","Someone observes everything in secret.","Graffiti on the corner of the blackboard.","Lily petals dance in the air in concert with the gentle breeze.","Limitless possibilities are now lying in your hand.","The legendary hand-made lunch box that can charge your Mahjong power.","A holiday without pre-arranged matches, how about chilling at the pool?","With the beach ball swaying before your eyes, your eyelids get heavier and heavier on this dozy afternoon.","The world now belongs to me! In my name, I command you: Obey me, world!","The king has returned, and those who can challenge my rule no longer exist!","This is the path of glorification a nameless hero has walked.","This is the path of initiation that started with a contract.","This is the path of transgression built upon lies.","Pseudo-magical circuit conversion...\nComplete! This is my all!","The shining stars of human history, coming down as miracles that help the girls turn the tide of the battle.","A riichi bet specially made based on Illya\'s request. One always imagines hearing a weird laughter coming from it without reason...","The bond between Magical Girls can overcome even dimensional barriers that are as wide as the galaxy.","According to Miyu, this is her partner. The sapphire blue color exudes a calm and mature aura.","Callous and ruthless, eliminating the target with just one shot—that\'s the way of the outlaw.","The shooting star, bearing the wishes of many, leaves an iridescent trail in the night sky.","A wandering predator from the desert, no one knows how it appeared on the mahjong table.","The sound of prayers waits for a response in the blue sky.","A mascot of unknown origin, true fans can talk about it all day.","A dark, beautiful, and deadly feast.","A shadow void that can engulf even fate.","The true name of the celebrated miracle.","A solemn and lonely justice.","Light that has been inverted and dyed pitch black.","With this winning hand and a Justaway... I\'ll send you flying!","Let\'s get \'em, Elizabeth!","HEY! Since when did my description change from \"the guy who wears glasses\" to the glasses themselves?!","Sunset, sea breeze, and a scooter-riding sweet tooth.","A Justaway tile is a Justaway tile. Nothing more, nothing less.","Elizabeth holds up a placard that reads: \"Ron!\"","牌背-官方赛事","桌布-官方赛事麒麟战","桌布-官方赛事四象战","Tablecloth - Official Tournament","Trial PT","Christmas Gift - Bells","Christmas Gift - Stocking","Lunar New Year event item.","Lunar New Year event item.","An instruction tool awarded after completing Nikaidou\'s Class.","A pair of glasses awarded after completing Nikaidou\'s Class.","Ichihime asked Nadeshiko to hang this wind chimes in the shrine.","Let\'s have some ice cream!!!","Watermelon slices prepared by Riu, the word says they are prepared for Chiori.","An item used for redeeming gifts from Moon Palace. It says \'No Underage Drinking\' on its bottom, but Ichihime sips it anyway. \"Sipping is not drinking, nyaa~\"","An item used for redeeming gifts from Moon Palace. Please keep Ichihime busy for the period that you are stocking these mooncakes.","Halloween Token. \"Nobody can escape my witchcraft~\" (Nobody: ???)","Halloween Token.\"Hek, hek, hek, wanna 